  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the events in the input trace
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ca.uqac.lif.cep.Duplicable, ca.uqac.lif.cep.functions.DuplicableFunction

    public class ProcessorVectorFunction<T>
extends VectorFunction<T>
    Vector function derived from a processor outputting numerical values. Given a sequence, the function feeds all its events to some given processor p, and creates a 1-dimensional DoublePoint with the last output of p.
